div.div:
Embracing a true Open Source philosophy is what keeps linkedin-cards alive and growing. 🚀
I'm excited to announce that support for video posts is now live! This major update wouldn't have been possible without the amazing contribution from Shihab Hasan. Huge thanks for your effort and for helping push this project forward. 🙌
The project is more active than ever, and I'd like to keep this momentum going. If you are looking to contribute, whether it's adding support for reposts or polishing the UI, I'd love to see your Pull Requests.
Check out the new feature and join the project here: https://lnkd.in/ek7q9sHg
#OpenSource #GitHub #Community #DeveloperTools #LinkedInCards
